{"tid":2431974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【曾連續25年排首位】香港遭DQ全球自由經濟體　傳統基金會不再獨立評級","createTime":"2021-03-04T04:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T06:52:33.000Z","uid":5195,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"caca6b1422e4854c809fedbba6df09a0f4edb667","tid":2431974,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"美國傳統基金會公佈2021年全球經濟自由度指數（Index of Economic Freedom），但過去連續25排首位、去年全球排第二的香港日後不再獨立評分，香港與澳門與排107位的中國一齊評分，令香港失卻一個重要經濟自由的評分。與此同時，新加坡繼續蟬聯全球最自由經濟體評分。<br />\n<br />\n傳統基金會在報告解釋，只會計算獨立主權國的經濟自由，雖然香港與澳門作為特別行政區，與大部分中國大陸民眾享有不同及較多的經濟自由，但「近年的發展毫不含糊地顯示，這些經濟政策最終由北京控制」（developments in recent years have demonstrated unambiguously that those policies are ultimately controlled from Beijing）。<br />\n<br />\n基金會在報告續說：「日後有需要的話，香港及澳門經濟自由發展會在指數有關中國篇幅中討論。」（As appropriate in the future, developments in Hong Kong or Macau that are relevant to economic freedom will be considered in the context of China&rsquo;s evaluation in the Index.）"},{"pid":"079629ca76a1c4ab09698323a9b4fcb604274e5b","tid":2431974,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkcnews.com/article/38816/%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83-38816/%E3%80%90%E6%9B%BE%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C25%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%92%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%ADdq%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%AB%94-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A?fbclid=IwAR15R5w_JuO1kdWvjrWKvzDeJrOjKj_vNLh8H_eYtZ_rMOwKtB4cMA2_53Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F38816%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%259C%2583-38816%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C25%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BD%258D%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%25ADdq%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%2